 ||| React 起源于 Facebook 的内部项目，因为该公司对市场上所有 JavaScript MVC 框架，都不满意，就决定自己写一套，用来架设Instagram 的网站。做出来以后，发现这套东西很好用，就在2013年5月开源了。 ||| React originated as an internal project at Facebook. Because the company was unsatisfied with all existing JavaScript MVC frameworks on the market, they decided to write their own to build the Instagram website. Once built, they found it very useful and open-sourced it in May 2013.
