 ||| 现在的web项目几乎都会用到spring框架，而要使用spring难免需要配置大量的xml配置文件，而 springboot的出现解   决了这一问题，一个项目甚至不用部署到服务器上直接开跑，真像springboot所说：“just run”。 ||| Almost all current web projects use the Spring framework, and using Spring inevitably requires configuring a large number of XML configuration files. The emergence of Spring Boot solved this problem; a project does not even need to be deployed to a server and can be run directly, just as Spring Boot says: "just run".
